Lois Wilson (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lois_Wilson_(actress) 0 Lois Wilson (June 28, 1894 – March 3, 1988) was an American actress who worked during the silent film era. She also directed two short films and was a scenario writer. Lois_Wilson ( June_28_,_1894 – March_3_,_1988 ) was an_American_actress who worked during the_silent_film_era .
